

## üß™ REST API Endpoints

> üîó **Base URL:** `http://localhost:5000`

---

### üì¶ Product APIs (`/product`)

| Method | Endpoint       | Description                     | Body Params               |
| ------ | -------------- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| GET    | `/product`     | Get all products                | ‚Äì                         |
| GET    | `/product/:id` | Get product by ID               | ‚Äì                         |
| POST   | `/product`     | Add a new product with image(s) | ‚úÖ `form-data` (see below) |
| PUT    | `/product/:id` | Update a product by ID          | ‚úÖ Yes                     |
| DELETE | `/product/:id` | Delete a product by ID          | ‚Äì                         |

#### üì§ POST `/product` (with images)

Use `multipart/form-data` with the following fields:

| Field    | Type     | Description                 |
| -------- | -------- | --------------------------- |
| id       | Number   | Product ID                  |
| name     | String   | Product name                |
| sku      | String   | SKU                         |
| desc     | String   | Description                 |
| price    | Number   | Price                       |
| discount | String   | Discount                    |
| material | String   | Material (e.g., "14K Gold") |
| stock    | Boolean  | In stock or not             |
| rating   | Number   | Rating (e.g., 4.5)          |
| reviews  | Number   | Number of reviews           |
| category | ObjectId | Category ID (MongoDB ID)    |
| **img**  | File(s)  | Upload multiple image files |

‚úÖ Images will be saved in `/upload`, and URLs will look like:
`http://localhost:5000/upload/<filename>`

---

### üóÇÔ∏è Category APIs (`/category`)

| Method | Endpoint        | Description        | Body Params |
| ------ | --------------- | ------------------ | ----------- |
| GET    | `/category`     | Get all categories | ‚Äì           |
| GET    | `/category/:id` | Get category by ID | ‚Äì           |
| POST   | `/category`     | Add a new category | ‚úÖ Yes       |
| PUT    | `/category/:id` | Update a category  | ‚úÖ Yes       |
| DELETE | `/category/:id` | Delete a category  | ‚Äì           |

**POST / PUT body example (JSON):**

```json
{
  "name": "Rings",
  "description": "All ring collections"
}
```

